Vim to learn:

Topics:
Registers

insert

:r ![cmd / file] --> write stdout of cmd or file to buffer
"gi" return to last insert
^t / ^d --> tab / untab

navigation

** USE THIS DAMMIT **
<C-o> / <C-i> go back/forward in "jumps"
*************

"zt" cursor top
"zb" cursor bottom
"m{key}" bookmark cursor
"`{key}" go to bookmark
|zN<CR>|	z{height}<CR>	   redraw, make window {height} lines high
|zf|		zf{motion}	   create a fold for Nmove text
|za|		za		   open a closed fold, close an open fold
